{"tid":1148761,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"而家仲有無人買樓投資？比15%稅值得嗎？","createTime":"2019-05-10T16:05:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T14:28:10.000Z","uid":58287,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6169e1000536a1e51cb4d3f67c627d7d642f3043","tid":1148761,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:05:50.000Z","msg":"而家買樓投資既人，係有人頭定15%稅都照比呢？<br />\n想了解下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df96ca36e969dd69e9fe2f62cc3160174393ca2","tid":1148761,"uid":5267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"174cbeb89668a4016e8e5ce3c422e748b4bb1ae5","tid":1148761,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a3c140de46021e7ecc9fd37efbd86f78ec650f6","tid":1148761,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"174cbeb89668a4016e8e5ce3c422e748b4bb1ae5","tid":1148761,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"照咁計，再扣埋利息開支，3年都要7%，即係得返20%。<br />\n<br />\n20／3＝6.67%年回報。<br />\n<br />\n好似買債或者HSBC收息仲實際。"},{"pid":"62c8ff00ed3970d75bd11fc19e283fd034516dae","tid":1148761,"uid":228794,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8a3c140de46021e7ecc9fd37efbd86f78ec650f6","tid":1148761,"uid":58287,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"174cbeb89668a4016e8e5ce3c422e748b4bb1ae5","tid":1148761,"uid":5267,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T16:16:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T02:52:06.000Z","msg":"照咁計，再扣埋利息開支，3年都要7%，即係得返20%。<br />\n<br />\n20／3＝6.67%年回報。<br />\n<br />\n好似買債或者HSBC收息仲實際。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"1）槓桿原理<br />\n2）收租"},{"pid":"fef056c1e565671b8d773ddeb89c7a93936ad700","tid":1148761,"uid":143142,"like":